  def my_pipeline():
      create_artifact_with_metadata(
          metadata={'foo': 'bar'},
          executor_output_destination=dsl.PIPELINE_TASK_EXECUTOR_OUTPUT_PATH_PLACEHOLDER,
      )
  ```

